{"title":"赞红星","authors":["孙维亮"],"dates":[{"year":1974,"month":10,"day":11}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"赞红星"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京西四北小学辅导员"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孙维亮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天上星，亮晶晶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比不上闪闪红五星。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爸爸头戴红星去长征，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"征途万里方向明。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈心红似红星，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掩护群众献生命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烈士虽死精神在，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唤起人民举红缨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党的儿子潘小冬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手捧红星心中红日升。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敢于革命挑重担，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风吹雨打松更青。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红小兵，爱红星，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命传统记心中。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一代新人举红旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远跟党干革命。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":3,"page_end":3}